# Creates Quiz questions & answers
Quiz.create([{question:"If you were playing in the World Cup--are you the player passing the ball or making the goals?", answer_1:"Making the goals.", answer_2:"Passing the ball."}, {question:"You’ve been late to work every other day this week and now today, your train is running 10 minutes late. Do you:", answer_1:"Tell everyone within earshot how irritated you are with MTA.", answer_2:"Wait patiently and continue bopping along to your favorite song." }, {question:"You’re having a party, and your friend asks you to put out a bag of chips for the guests. Do you:", answer_1:"Hold the chip bag and eat directly from it.", answer_2:"Put the chips in the party bowl." }, {question: "When entering a restaurant, you’re the one:", answer_1:"Telling the host how many people are in your party.", answer_2:"Hanging back until the rest of your friends get through the door."},{question: "You have an interview for your dream job. You feel:", answer_1:"Freaked out! So much at stake.", answer_2: "You’ve been waiting for this kind of opportunity."},{question: "You’re at a party and it’s kind of lame, do you:", answer_1: "Find a new party to go and text your friends the new location.", answer_2: "Wait until your friend is ready to go."}])
